  <object name="lobby">
    <inherit name="editor_room" />
    <description><![CDATA[The lobby is a plain but functional room outside the main meeting hall of the village. In keeping with the darkness of Ignarus, the room is dimly lit. Swords decorate the walls as a warning to those who would trespass in this government building. A fancy wooden door is set into the north wall. When you enter, a purple door swings shut behind you with a heavy click.<br/><br/>For all that, the people here are more cheerful than in other villages you have visited in Ignarus. You can hear friendly chatter from rooms on either side. Ignarus may be a dictatorship, but here in the village of Somed, the people still run their <b>local government</b> as a <b>democracy.</b> As long as King Nocens doesn't find out, everything should be just fine...]]></description>
    <attr name="grid_width" type="int">2</attr>
    <attr name="grid_length" type="int">2</attr>
