  <object name="Meeting Chamber">
    <inherit name="editor_room" />
    <description><![CDATA[This is a huge, echoing chamber shaped like a hexagon. The polished walls shine in the candlelight. A massive circular table sits in the center of the room, surrounded by eight empty stools. Each stool has a sign in front of it. There is one red chair with a plaque reading MAYOR on its arm.<br/><br/>Benches line the walls around the chamber. Although they are currently empty, you can tell that many people have sat in them over the years, enjoying the right to participate in democracy -- even if they have to do it secretly so King Nocens won't find out the truth!<br/><br/>There are many doors in this room, each decorated slightly differently. To the north, there is a tiny door so small it might have been made for a hobbit. There is a poster tacked up beside the tiny door.<br/><br/><b>HINT: There are a few things to do in this room. Try using different objects and exploring! </b>]]></description>
    <attr name="grid_width" type="int">5</attr>
    <attr name="grid_length" type="int">5</attr>
    <attr name="grid_fill">SkyBlue</attr>
