    <object name="plaque">
      <inherit name="editor_object" />
      <alt type="stringlist">
        <value>plaques</value>
      </alt>
      <look>Each of the signs is labeled "city councilor." There are enough seats for seven councillors, plus the red mayor's chair at the head of the table.</look>
      <examine>The plaque reads MAYOR, clearly identifying the red chair as belonging to the town council's leader.</examine>
      <touch>It is cool. Your fingertips leave smudges on the polished brass.</touch>
      <scenery />
      <displayverbs type="stringlist">
        <value>Look at</value>
      </displayverbs>
      <read>The plaque reads MAYOR, clearly identifying the red chair as belonging to the town council's leader.</read>
