      <look><![CDATA[A worn piece of parchment sits next to the tiny door.<br/><br/>It reads:<br/><br/><i> This door is closed and locked to all<br/>Who wish to leave this special hall<br/>If you would view our secret lair<br/>Sit and TWIRL the leader's chair </i>]]></look>
