  <object name="secret chamber">
    <inherit name="editor_room" />
    <alias>Secret Chamber</alias>
    <description><![CDATA[This is a small chamber. The ceiling is so low you almost bump your head ducking through the door. You can see four robed figures, each holding a candle: a green robed figure with a green candle, a red robed figure with a red candle, a blue robed figure with a blue candle, and a yellow robed figure with a yellow candle. Each stands in a corner of the room. Behind them is a wooden door. It almost seems to glow.<br/><br/><b>HINT: You will need to talk to each of these figures. You will also need to give them something. To use the GIVE command, type GIVE ____ to _____ (for example, give money to red figure). <i> It will not work </i> if you type "give the red figure the money." </b><br/><br/>]]></description>
    <attr name="grid_fill">SlateGray</attr>
    <exit alias="south" to="Meeting Chamber">
      <inherit name="southdirection" />
    </exit>
