  <object name="chamber of taxation">
    <inherit name="editor_room" />
    <alias>Chamber of Taxation</alias>
    <description><![CDATA[This is a small rom with four or five desks. Each one has a pile of papers. Some are messy, some are organized. A sign hanging over the door proclaims the room to be the <b>Chamber of Taxation.</b><br/><br/>A small elvish woman sits at the furthest desk, writing frantically. There are piles of gold on the table, and her hand is covered in ink. <br/><br/>There is a large pile of gold behind her. At the top you can see a strange gold coin that looks like someone took a bite out of it.<br/><br/><b>HINT: You will need to talk to this elf! Try typing "talk to the elf," or "ask the elf about _______." If you want to give her something, try "give ____ to the elf." </b>]]></description>
    <attr name="grid_width" type="int">2</attr>
    <attr name="grid_length" type="int">2</attr>
    <attr name="grid_fill">SpringGreen</attr>
